WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:11.059
Hey, good morning family. Thank you for joining me today. It's just me today, but I'm excited to be here, and I pray you are too.

00:00:11.060 --> 00:00:23.399
Yesterday, when Diana and I were praying over the things the Lord had for us, it was over the top. The presence of the Lord was tangible in this house.

00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:34.770
The Lord showed me again one last call; His eyes were looking over the horizon at the sheep that were lost.

00:00:34.771 --> 00:00:47.594
He would leave the 99 and go after the one. I could see Him longing for His lost child, the lost ones, the wayward people in the backfields.

00:00:47.595 --> 00:00:57.716
He's coming for you. I believe even Braden loved it when the Lord said, "The devil came at the youth hard, but I'm going to come at them harder.

00:00:57.717 --> 00:01:11.403
I'm coming for the youth of this generation."He said, "I'm coming back for a glorious church,"but man, what the Lord has in store for the youth!

00:01:11.404 --> 00:01:22.038
I believe we're about to see some of the greatest moves of the Spirit of the Lord we've ever seen before—demonstrations and manifestations of the glory of God.

00:01:22.039 --> 00:01:28.326
I know the Bible says there's a great falling away. I understand that, but I know what He also said to me.

00:01:28.327 --> 00:01:37.673
He said, "Brandon, I'm coming for the one."Do you realize how much Jesus loves you today?

00:01:37.674 --> 00:01:45.357
Do you realize how much He has a plan for your life? Every single one of you, He loves.

00:01:45.358 --> 00:01:57.077
When we go through a major city and I see all the people, I think, "Isn't it amazing that He has interest in every single one of us?"There are millions and billions of us.

00:01:57.078 --> 00:02:05.605
There are only 300-some million people in the United States; around the world, there are billions.

00:02:05.606 --> 00:02:11.954
Think about that. He has a plan, and He knows every hair on your head.

00:02:11.955 --> 00:02:17.308
He knows your past, He knows your future, and He knows everything about you.

00:02:17.309 --> 00:02:27.579
He knows the day you're going to take your last breath, but He wants every one of you to know Him. That's exciting.

00:02:27.580 --> 00:02:34.357
It's overwhelming to me to think that He has a plan for every single one of us and that He knows us all that well.

00:02:34.358 --> 00:02:45.114
He knows all our faults and our pains; He knows what you're bad at and what you're good at. It's amazing. God is a good God. I was excited.

00:02:45.115 --> 00:02:54.649
A lot of people say, "What does Sooner mean?"or "What did you see, Sooner?"I believe it is a representation of the land run.

00:02:54.650 --> 00:03:10.994
If you look at what the Sooners do—the same reason why they named the college the Oklahoma Sooners—He highlighted "Sooners"in an arch before me.

00:03:10.995 --> 00:03:19.878
He was talking about Japan and South Korea, and I thought that was interesting because He highlighted that to me.

00:03:19.879 --> 00:03:28.394
People say, "How do you see all this? Oh, you just have a great imagination, Brandon."I'm not that good, I'll be real with y'all.

00:03:28.395 --> 00:03:43.466
If you realized who is talking to you behind the camera, you would go, "Wow."Seriously, I think it's amazing the things the Lord will show us in prayer if you seek Him.

00:03:43.468 --> 00:03:51.459
When He talked about Iraq again, people say, "Well, are you talking about the revaluation of the Iraqi dinar?"I have no idea.

00:03:51.460 --> 00:04:03.050
When I'm in the Spirit like that and saying what I'm seeing, I don't remember a lot of what I'm saying because I'm flowing with the Holy Ghost.

00:04:03.052 --> 00:04:18.407
So my son and my wife will say, "This is what you said,"because Diana or Braden takes notes of everything the Lord shows me whenever I'm praying; that's what we do in our private time.

00:04:18.408 --> 00:04:25.992
We're just doing more private time in public view so people can see us and how the Lord flows.

00:04:25.993 --> 00:04:31.261
This is what we do on a day-to-day basis. This is how serious we take it.

00:04:31.262 --> 00:04:38.631
The Holy Spirit visits us like this all the time. I'm not bragging; it's just real.

00:04:38.632 --> 00:04:43.452
He will show us that which is to come. This is how the Trump ear prophecy came out.

00:04:43.452 --> 00:05:00.007
This is how saying there would be a red wave or XRP, and all these things He's showing me about wars and the plague—it is all birthed out of prayer.

00:05:00.008 --> 00:05:10.354
I don't just walk around and get these prophetic words. I told you, I don't feel like I walk in a prophetic gift; I'm a watchman.

00:05:10.355 --> 00:05:25.875
It's totally different than somebody who walks around saying, "I hear the voice of the Lord."That's amazing when it happens, don't get me wrong, but I see when I pray in the Spirit, not in English.

00:05:25.876 --> 00:05:34.088
Even my kids say, "Dad prays in tongues and Dad prays a lot in tongues, and that's what we do."I get in the car and drive around, and the Lord shows me things: open-eyed visions.

00:05:34.089 --> 00:05:39.772
I don't close my eyes when I'm driving around and run into somebody!

00:05:39.773 --> 00:05:43.839
I'm praying and looking, and all of a sudden, He'll show me an open-eyed vision.

00:05:43.840 --> 00:05:48.595
I'll see things, and the Lord will show me that which is to come. I believe that's a gift.

00:05:48.596 --> 00:05:54.559
I believe God gives those gifts to intercessory prayer people—people who intercede for the nations.

00:05:54.560 --> 00:06:01.696
They intercede and are prayer people. I believe that He's no respecter of persons; what He'll do for me, He'll do for you.

00:06:01.697 --> 00:06:14.546
I say it all the time: "Father, give me eyes to see what I need to see and ears for what I need to hear."I thank You, Lord, that I am never snared by any satanic or demonic force.

00:06:14.547 --> 00:06:22.952
I thank You, Father, that no weapon formed against me will prosper, but I hear Your voice, and a stranger's voice I will not follow.

00:06:22.953 --> 00:06:32.716
I hear You, Father; You speak to me and show me that which is to come as I sit on the wall. That's what I do.

00:06:32.717 --> 00:06:41.030
I confess that over myself all the time: I hear and see what the Father wants me to see. And I take communion.

00:06:41.031 --> 00:06:49.658
I have these communion cups—we've got communion everywhere: the living room, the kitchen, the bedrooms.

00:06:49.659 --> 00:06:55.872
We have it in the car. We go before the Lord with communion all the time.

00:06:55.873 --> 00:07:05.677
We like it so much, I told y'all I'm turning purple! It's just funny to us because we say we're turning purple.

00:07:05.678 --> 00:07:12.318
Billy Burke says that: "I turn purple, I turn purple,"because we take communion so much.

00:07:12.319 --> 00:07:17.743
We believe in the anointing and the power of the Holy Spirit.

00:07:17.744 --> 00:07:25.286
We believe Jesus Christ has chosen us and we are called to the kingdom for such a time as this. We're excited you're here.

00:07:25.287 --> 00:07:31.445
We're believing for a million-man and woman prayer army to pray on this channel, as He told us.

00:07:31.446 --> 00:07:41.882
He said, "Brandon, you do this and we can change the course of governments and things all around us."So we saw about that yesterday.

00:07:41.883 --> 00:07:53.679
We saw the Sooners and the things we prayed about Iraq. I told you about the attacks; I said we're praying against attacks against our bases—our army bases and naval bases in Iraq.

00:07:53.680 --> 00:08:00.638
I'm not familiar with them, but I saw bases being targets for war.

00:08:00.639 --> 00:08:13.032
So we pray against that and for the Houthis, that they will not be able to hurt any of our service people, that they're always in the right place at the right time, and no weapon formed against them will prosper.

00:08:13.033 --> 00:08:25.172
We pray over that. I've prayed over what the Lord showed me about Kim Jong-un, the troops going over in the train, and the war trying to escalate.

00:08:25.173 --> 00:08:37.679
I see it. Then we were praying over... there was a lot. We had our list, but I thought, "Well, what's fresh today?"If the Lord shows us something today, cool.

00:08:37.680 --> 00:08:45.476
If he doesn't, I always go with anticipation that God is going to show up and show off and show us what he wants us to see.

00:08:45.477 --> 00:08:49.760
So, we pray you're excited. We pray you want to be a part of this.

00:08:49.761 --> 00:08:53.399
And let's just get started. So, we always take communion to start off.

00:08:53.400 --> 00:08:58.719
I always enter by the blood of the Lamb, by the word of our testimony.

00:08:58.720 --> 00:09:04.154
Thank you, Father, for all that you've done. Thank you, Father, for all that you've done for us.

00:09:04.155 --> 00:09:08.944
I thank you, God, that you set us free by the blood. You said you were wounded for our transgressions.

00:09:08.945 --> 00:09:13.456
You were bruised for our iniquities. The chastisement of our peace was upon you.

00:09:13.457 --> 00:09:19.274
And with your stripes, we are healed. And Father, we thank you, Lord, for your body that was broken for us today.

00:09:19.275 --> 00:09:24.450
And we take this body and we thank you, Lord, that by your stripes, we are healed.

00:09:24.451 --> 00:09:31.631
And we take it right now in the name of Jesus. And we are healed from the top of our head to the soles of our feet.

00:09:31.632 --> 00:09:38.350
And we're expecting the manifestation of what we've been believing for now in Jesus'name.

00:09:38.351 --> 00:09:42.754
Father, we thank you, Lord, that we're delivered. We're delivered from all bondage.

00:09:42.755 --> 00:10:00.609
We're delivered in Jesus'name. And we thank you, Father, for it. Lord, we plead the blood of Jesus over us.

00:10:00.610 --> 00:10:08.084
You said in your word, if we confess our sin, you're faithful and just to forgive us of our sin and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

00:10:08.085 --> 00:10:17.006
And we plead the blood of Jesus over us today, God. And we thank you, Lord, for we make much of the blood, and the blood will make much of us.

00:10:17.007 --> 00:10:32.390
And we plead the blood of Jesus Christ over us today. And we thank you, Father, that it is well with us in our soul. And we come up higher with the fire.

00:10:32.391 --> 00:10:45.416
And we see from an eagle's eye, not down on the lower level, but Father, we come up higher with you on the higher level, seated with you in the heavenlies.

00:10:45.417 --> 00:10:51.219
And we take our seat. We take our rightful place with you right now in the name of Jesus.

00:10:51.220 --> 00:10:56.436
And we thank you, Lord, that you're making intercession for us at the right hand of the Father.

00:10:56.437 --> 00:11:01.618
And we take this blood right now and we plead the blood of Jesus Christ over us.

00:11:01.619 --> 00:11:08.043
And we thank you, Father, that what you bore in your body, we don't have to bear in our own.

00:11:08.044 --> 00:11:14.210
We're healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus. And we thank you, Father, for all that you've done for us.

00:11:14.211 --> 00:11:17.308
Thank you for your blood. Thank you, Lord, for what you've done.

00:11:17.309 --> 00:11:22.579
Glory to your name, Lord. We're expecting and we'll be used by you.

00:11:22.580 --> 00:11:27.599
We'll be filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost because we say yes.

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:31.273
Just like yesterday, he said, 'Who will say yes?'We say yes.

00:11:31.274 --> 00:11:51.017
We say yes today, Lord. In Jesus'name. Lord, we thank you. The news is saying there's a rat in the White House.

00:11:51.018 --> 00:12:04.896
I've heard that before. Lord, you warned us about the rat. You warned us about the people trying to sabotage and do the things that they're trying to do.

00:12:04.897 --> 00:12:11.838
And Father, I thank you, Lord, that the rats are found and caught in the cages that they need to be in.

00:12:11.839 --> 00:12:23.614
I thank you, Father, that you're exposing the rats. You're exposing the people that I've seen that are trying to bring down this government.

00:12:23.615 --> 00:12:28.585
Father, your angels are going before us and they're preparing the way.

00:12:28.586 --> 00:12:34.359
I send them out right now in the name of Jesus from the north, the south, the east, the west.

00:12:34.360 --> 00:12:44.380
We call our angels, Father, to war on our behalf today. We thank you, Lord, that your warring angel armies are warring on our behalf.

00:12:44.381 --> 00:12:54.179
Father, you said we will work with them. And Father, I thank you, Lord, that we will work with them and we commission them to go forth now in the name of Jesus.

00:12:54.180 --> 00:13:01.388
And we thank you, Lord, that they are bearing us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:13:01.389 --> 00:13:11.537
And I pray over President Trump right now in the name of Jesus that he has great discernment.

00:13:11.538 --> 00:13:25.748
And Father, he will hear you even in the midnight hour of knowing who to put around him, God, that he would know who are the rats and who is there to be trusted, Father.

00:13:25.749 --> 00:13:31.482
That he'll not be snared by his own pride or anything of the flesh; that he would hear you, God.

00:13:31.483 --> 00:13:36.903
He would be humbled before you, Father. That he would humble himself underneath the mighty hand.

00:13:36.904 --> 00:13:45.118
And in due time, he will be exalted. And Lord, he's been exalted into his position of authority over America.

00:13:45.119 --> 00:14:00.766
So Father, I thank you, Lord, that you protect our leader, that you undergird him, Father, that he would have the wisdom to lead this great nation back to victory, Father, delivering us out of the hand of the evil.

00:14:00.767 --> 00:14:09.988
That Father, he is delivered out of the hand of the darkness, that he is not being influenced by any satanic or demonic force.

00:14:09.989 --> 00:14:18.896
I thank you, Lord, for JD Vance, his wife, and his children, and over President Trump, his children, and Melania.

00:14:18.897 --> 00:14:23.035
I pray a hedge of protection around every single one of them.

00:14:23.036 --> 00:14:35.344
Father, I thank you, Lord, for our leaders in Congress and our House, that there will be a radical move of the presence of the Lord, a radical move of the Lord on the Senate and the House floor.

00:14:35.345 --> 00:14:44.677
That we will have revival. So, Father, we thank you, Lord, for every judge and every person that's represented in the Congress and in the Senate.

00:14:44.678 --> 00:14:58.193
Father, I pray over them right now in the name of Jesus for making godly laws, that there'll be a supernatural hand of the Holy Ghost on our nation once again for one last call. Father, I thank you, Lord.

00:14:58.194 --> 00:15:12.638
I know that you showed me a great financial crash, but Lord, you said to me, 'Brandon, what the prayers prayed in October, the things that were prayed in October, I'm giving you extended time.

00:15:12.639 --> 00:15:20.060
I'm giving you a season of grace for a great wealth transfer will come on the ones that are listening, on the 1%.

00:15:20.061 --> 00:15:31.185
And as they hear me, they will be provided for.'There will be a great shaking to awaken over America, for they will be humbled.

00:15:31.186 --> 00:15:37.166
America will be humbled in the days ahead. When, I don't know, but Lord, you said it was coming.

00:15:37.167 --> 00:15:43.979
But I know that we will not be caught off guard. It's not for us to be caught off guard. Father, we pray mercy.

00:15:43.980 --> 00:15:50.141
Just like Abraham interceded on behalf of Sodom and Gomorrah, we intercede on behalf of America.

00:15:50.142 --> 00:16:01.257
And Father, we don't want to not have a shaking to awaken because Father, to keep going down the same road and wanting different results is insanity.

00:16:01.258 --> 00:16:07.278
You have to have something to change it. And we thank you, Lord, that there's a changing of the tide.

00:16:07.279 --> 00:16:13.893
There's a changing of circumstances to shake the people out of the slumber.

00:16:13.894 --> 00:16:27.483
And Father, I thank you, Lord, it's not just for the body of Christ, but Father, the ones in the back field, to shake them out of their slumber. And what more to do it, Father, than you? You'll do this.

00:16:27.484 --> 00:16:44.879
And Father, I thank you, Lord, that this is a time like we've never seen before for the greatest outpouring, the greatest radical outpouring of the Spirit of the Lord, more than what we've ever seen before on this earth, more than any time, more than any other place all throughout eternity.

00:16:44.880 --> 00:16:50.647
Father, we've come to this time, the end of the end. And Father, we were born in this time.

00:16:50.648 --> 00:16:57.354
And Father, you've called us for this time. And Father, I thank you that we please you.

00:16:57.355 --> 00:17:03.104
You say, 'Well done, thy good and faithful servant. Go and enter into my rest.'Thank you, Lord, that that's who we are.

00:17:03.105 --> 00:17:08.606
We will be the ones that close this thing up. We're the closers.

00:17:08.607 --> 00:17:13.033
Every single one of us right now that are born into this generation are closers.

00:17:13.034 --> 00:17:18.338
And we will be the closers. It wasn't brother Hagin. It wasn't Oral Roberts.

00:17:18.339 --> 00:17:25.714
It wasn't Kathryn Kuhlman. It was us. You called us for now. They were the generation before the end of all.

00:17:25.715 --> 00:17:29.962
And now you've called us, Lord, and we're going to finish the race.

00:17:29.963 --> 00:17:36.451
They passed the baton, and as they pass the baton, we're running with the relay race baton.

00:17:36.452 --> 00:17:46.960
And we're running and we're going to finish that way. We see the finish line ahead of us, Lord, and we want to finish strong. We want to live long and finish strong.

00:17:46.961 --> 00:18:01.117
We want to finish the race with great victory and not just barely passing by over that finish line going, "Well, we made it."No, we go running and we break records.

00:18:01.118 --> 00:18:08.247
We're barrier breakers. We have a barrier breaker anointing on the inside of us and a barrier breaker mentality.

00:18:08.248 --> 00:18:11.514
We don't have a "just give up, barely getting by"mentality.

00:18:11.515 --> 00:18:17.776
We have a mentality of saying we can do all things through Christ who strengthens us.

00:18:17.777 --> 00:18:25.036
We can do all things, for you've given us strength and a hope. I believe, Father, that we'll be the barrier breakers.

00:18:25.037 --> 00:18:36.523
Where Billy Graham went and saved hundreds of thousands in a meeting, Father, it will be more on us: the greater anointing, a greater capacity, a greater revelation of your word.

00:18:36.524 --> 00:18:50.283
Father, I thank you, Lord, for supernatural wisdom concerning the word of God, that we would have an anointing of knowing how to teach and preach the word in a way that no generation has ever done before.

00:18:50.284 --> 00:18:58.243
I thank you, Father, that this is a time that we soar. We're coming up higher with the fire, Father.

00:18:58.244 --> 00:19:06.556
It'll be just like Moses; if you would do that for Moses in the old covenant, how much more will you do it for us in the new covenant?

00:19:06.557 --> 00:19:14.174
How much more, if you would do that for Elijah and Elisha, Father, how much more will you do it for us?

00:19:14.175 --> 00:19:19.251
We have a new covenant with new promises and the blood of Jesus.

00:19:19.252 --> 00:19:29.664
We believe, Father, that we receive the greater impartation that we've never seen on this earth before. Father, it would be on the sons and the daughters.

00:19:29.665 --> 00:19:37.535
You said in your word that you're going to pour out your spirit upon all flesh and your sons and your daughters will prophesy.

00:19:37.536 --> 00:19:47.268
And I believe that we're that generation that's closing it up, Father, just like you said last night, who will say yes.

00:19:47.269 --> 00:19:57.922
And Father, we will say yes. We will say yes to you, Father. We will seek you and we will find you. We will knock and the door will be opened unto us.

00:19:57.923 --> 00:20:11.359
You said, "Give, and it shall be given unto us: good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over will men give into our bosom."Father, I pray over every single person who has seed in the ground.

00:20:11.360 --> 00:20:16.916
Father, that their seed will multiply: some thirty, some sixty, and hundredfold.

00:20:16.917 --> 00:20:25.318
Father, we're thankful for the thirty and we're thankful for the sixty, but God, we're believing for the overflow. And overflow comes out of hundredfold ground.

00:20:25.319 --> 00:20:37.051
And I thank you, Lord, that we put our seed in hundredfold ground and we get forth that hundredfold harvest quickly—multiplication quickly in the name of Jesus.

00:20:37.052 --> 00:20:47.024
We break the bonds of poverty and all the lack and "not enough"and "barely getting by."We take authority over it in the name of Jesus and we break it off of our households.

00:20:47.025 --> 00:20:52.093
Father, that whatever we put our hands to will prosper in the name of Jesus.

00:20:52.094 --> 00:20:56.913
Father, that we'll have exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:20:56.914 --> 00:21:03.163
Father, this is not a time to shrink back, but it's a time to grab hold and take over the land.

00:21:03.164 --> 00:21:13.524
Father, I thank you, Lord, that we're taking the land just like Joshua and Caleb did; we're not going to be grasshoppers or be the size of grasshoppers to the giants.

00:21:13.525 --> 00:21:20.036
No! Who is that uncircumcised Philistine that he will try to defy the armies of the living God?

00:21:20.037 --> 00:21:23.638
We're going to take back the land and we're going to take it back strong.

00:21:23.639 --> 00:21:33.256
And we're going to take it back with all we've got, not being afraid of the terror of the night nor for the arrow that flieth by day.

00:21:33.257 --> 00:21:41.616
Father, we thank you, Lord, that we're taking our dominion and our authority, and we're going into all the world and we're preaching the gospel throughout the whole world.

00:21:41.617 --> 00:21:47.198
And you said when this gospel is preached throughout the whole world, then the end would come.

00:21:47.199 --> 00:21:54.086
I believe that, Father, we are called to preach the gospel throughout the whole world. And we're raising up our prayer force.

00:21:54.087 --> 00:22:06.269
We're raising up an army of great believers on this platform, and they're going—from Africa, Asia, South America, and all over Europe.

00:22:06.270 --> 00:22:16.594
Father, I thank you, Lord, that there'll be a great harvest of souls come through this channel and we will touch this generation one more time for you, Jesus.

00:22:16.595 --> 00:22:24.558
We'll do it. We're not going to shy back and be afraid. We're not going to be intimidated by what they think about us.

00:22:24.559 --> 00:22:28.908
We don't care about what they think about us; we only care about what you think about us.

00:22:28.909 --> 00:22:38.479
And you said, "Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health even as your soul prospers."You said you have a great future for us and an expected end.

00:22:38.480 --> 00:22:45.390
Father, it's never for us to go just barely getting by; it's to have the overflow.

00:22:45.391 --> 00:22:57.810
Not just about finances, but the glory. The glorious church will rise without spot or wrinkle in these last days.

00:22:57.811 --> 00:23:06.065
Like Tommy Hicks'vision said, when the giant points his finger at us, we don't shrink back and say no.

00:23:06.066 --> 00:23:26.011
We say, "Yes Lord, here am I. Yes Lord, here are we. Send us."When he put the fire from the altar on his lips: "Here am I, Lord, send me."I thank you, Lord.

00:23:26.012 --> 00:23:33.111
It's just like a fire shut up in my bones—a Holy Ghost fire shut up in my bones.

00:23:33.112 --> 00:23:48.423
I believe there's fire on the inside of me, burning and keeping me alive, stirring me up. And there's a new wine and new wine skin.

00:23:48.424 --> 00:23:57.302
And every one of us that has been dry and every one of us that is lacking a fresh water and a drink today, we call them stirred up in the name of Jesus.

00:23:57.303 --> 00:24:05.700
We break out of that pit of despair, the pit of hopelessness and "barely getting by"spiritually.

00:24:05.701 --> 00:24:12.158
It's time to thrive in '25. It's time to thrive spiritually in 2025.

00:24:12.159 --> 00:24:25.948
Get up and shake off that old beggar's cloak and get off of that old "barely getting by, always broke"mentality and say, "God, I'm going to do something big for you today."We're going to do something big for Jesus.

